  "story": "One of the most cherished Kannada Christian hymns, this keerthane is a direct echo of David's Psalms calling the soul to praise the Lord. It has been a staple in Karnataka Protestant churches since the Basel Mission era, sung with deep devotion as an opening or closing hymn in worship services.",
  "lyrics": {
